9. ‚ù§Ô∏èMassive inclusivity

Floor price of a Clone is 15.65 ETH ($45,800). Not everyone can afford that. But the team confirmed that you don‚Äôt need a Clone to enjoy the experience.  

Space/Loot Pods/MNLTH are great entry points. That includes more people into the metaverse. 

9/9

8. ü§© Building the metaverse, one Space Pod at a time

Instead of launching a token to raise funds to build an open metaverse, RTFKT has taken the approach to build from the ground up. Start from a small room, get the community involved, and move on to larger things. 

8/X

7. ü•µNike‚Äôs involvement in Loot Pods

Not much has been revealed about Nike‚Äôs roadmap with RTFKT and #CloneX but having Nike‚Äôs logos in Loot Pods and the #MNLTH is a sure sign that the sporting giant is 100% on board for an epic adventure. No messy NFT sale, no cash grab. 

7/X

6. üëãüèª Interactivity between members 

Multiplayer mode is going to be epic as members will be able to organize events (more Zen sessions, anyone?), parties, and chat rooms for the community. Foundation for a fantastic metaverse. 

6/X

5. ü§Ø More extensions?!?!!

Loot pods are only the first extension of many teased by the PodX system video. One can only wonder what other extensions members are going to get and how avatars can interact with the structure.

4. üåê Not restricted to existing metaverses

@RTFKTstudios tapping on the collective creativity. Check this out: https://t.co/5F6lttPq3t
